<li id="cite_note-36"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="Technological_singularity#cite_ref-36">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFMoravec,_Hans1999" class="citation book">Moravec, Hans (1999). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/?id=fduW6KHhWtQC&amp;pg=PA61"><i>Robot: Mere Machine to Transcendent Mind</i></a>. Oxford U. Press. p.&#160;61. <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0-19-513630-2" title="Special:BookSources/978-0-19-513630-2"><bdi>978-0-19-513630-2</bdi></a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Robot%3A+Mere+Machine+to+Transcendent+Mind&amp;rft.pages=61&amp;rft.pub=Oxford+U.+Press&amp;rft.date=1999&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-19-513630-2&amp;rft.au=Moravec%2C+Hans&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2F%3Fid%3DfduW6KHhWtQC%26pg%3DPA61&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ATechnological+singularity" class="Z3988"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r951705291"/></span>
